Cisco verifies the earner of this badge successfully completed the Hardware and Upgrade Support course. This course builds foundational knowledge for working safely with computer hardware. Learners practice safety procedures, identify ports and cables, assist users with device info, and troubleshoot common hardware issues. They also gain hands-on experience installing and upgrading components to support maintenance and perform essential computer repairs<br/><img src='/images/hardware and upgrade support.png' width='500' height='500'>
